BP Plans Flaring at Carson, California, Refinery Through Oct. 3

-- B y   J o e   C a r r o l l
-- 
2011-09-25T20:02:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/bp-plans-flaring-at-carson-california-refinery-through-oct-3.html
BP Plc (BP/)  plans flaring at its Carson,
 California , oil refinery from tomorrow through Oct. 3, according
to a company filing with the  South Coast Air Quality Management
District .  The flaring is expected to begin at 12:45 p.m. local time
tomorrow, London-based BP said in the filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joe Carroll in  Chicago  at 
 jcarroll8@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Susan Warren at 
 susanwarren@bloomberg.net . 